│                                                                                            │
│ Let's re-examine the logic. The vectorizer gathers a `BoUpSLP` tree. We can inspect the    │
│ leaves of this tree.                                                                       │
│                                                                                            │
│ The most direct fix is to prevent the vectorization of any scalar instruction that is used │
